{"tid":900773,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★700?】財困男留遺書　大廈天台墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-11-13T13:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T15:33:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df4f3cecddade4f8d33e3f2c20fb53d51cc7fdab","tid":900773,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"觀塘發生男子墮樓死亡案，一名47歲男子，今日(13日)傍晚6時許，被人發現從康寧道41號金橋華廈高處墮下，倒臥大廈一樓平台，重傷奄奄一息。救護員接報趕至，經檢驗後證實該男子已死亡。警方在場調查，在大廈天台檢獲一封遺書及死者隨身物品，死者並非大廈住客，<span style=\"color: red;\">近日飽受債務問題困擾</span>，不排除因此自尋短見，警方已聯絡死者家人了解情況，死者死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181113/bkn-20181113203716608-1113_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181113%2Fbkn-20181113203716608-1113_00822_001.html&d=YuHE%2FmQVi5mMJQIqXTrZGrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f2a0b3f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181113/bkn-20181113203716608-1113_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0412ae38acd9c291e44686aa9ae6a1328dd94f9e","tid":900773,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n財經台班樓主高高高有邊個無上水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d8d4f6e8b12ee51e8f846c9e92b2d8911df576","tid":900773,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0412ae38acd9c291e44686aa9ae6a1328dd94f9e","tid":900773,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n財經台班樓主高高高有邊個無上水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"